{"tid":1327492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大和解】點解警隊高層要推啲下屬出去比人打","createTime":"2019-07-17T15:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T00:34:53.000Z","uid":140738,"like":30,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1d32cdd97362f31452d19b0d2a96b078652081d1","tid":1327492,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千錯萬錯 都係啲高層嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n以沙田上水為例<br />\n<br />\n明明就係阿頭落錯order搞到自己比人打，<br />\n<br />\n七八點就諗住清場，仲要斷哂人所有後路，<br />\n<br />\n逼到人無路走啲人咪唯有開拖，搞到有不必要衝突！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果由班示威者玩到十二點一點<br />\n<br />\n尾班車之前已經散咁大半人啦，<br />\n<br />\n到時出黎攞返個尾彩，咪大家開心囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再講 嗰度民居黎<br />\n<br />\n大把人食完飯返緊屋企、出緊去食飯、路過食花生<br />\n<br />\n要清場不如直接宣布戒嚴宵禁啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以結論係，最錯都係班落order嘅警，<br />\n<br />\n你班藍衫人仇視示威者、打到啲示威者仆街之前，<br />\n<br />\n問下你老細點解要推你出黎打依啲無必要嘅交，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩各藍衫警唔好做隻忠心警犬</span></span>"},{"pid":"8f693c10084129ab29588738e2d886ba849e958a","tid":1327492,"uid":281153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c1da9237ec9f7f38e4c4495599ceb5ca9a90447","tid":1327492,"uid":256914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"我冇野講 <br />\n因為掛住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723f30f4ee6dc63b373f1414e322c0fd1cfaa497","tid":1327492,"uid":140738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07befa8c3ae8acc74e5b908ab3411e09bf0d5360","tid":1327492,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"加入我們 實踐抱負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\